      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nEnrollment funnel from SRG file receipt through FIS reconciliation. **Click any tile** to see detail. Sourced from `reporting.fact_enrollments`.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| Correlation ID | `fact_enrollments.correlation_id` | UUID linking all records from one SRG file |\n| SRG File Type | `fact_enrollments.srg_file_type` | SRG310=New \u00b7 SRG315=Update \u00b7 SRG320=Termination |\n| FIS Record Type | `fact_enrollments.fis_record_type` | RT30=New account \u00b7 RT37=Card update \u00b7 RT60=Fund load |\n| Processing Status | `fact_enrollments.processing_status` | STAGED \u2192 ACCEPTED \u2192 (FAILED) |\n\n**Pipeline:** SRG arrives \u2192 Stage 1 \u2192 Stage 2 \u2192 Stage 3 (STAGED) \u2192 Stage 5 (SCP) \u2192 Stage 7 (ACCEPTED/FAILED)",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
